These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, tea, fanta, coffee
Sport: rugby, skiing, parkour, snowboarding
1. Beverage:mirinda is on the right of Sport:parkour##1
2. Sport:snowboarding is on the far left##1
3. Sport:parkour is between Sport:skiing and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:fanta is between Beverage:tea and Beverage:mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee         | tea   | fanta | mirinda       |
| Sport      | snowboarding | rugby | parkour   | skiing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: hiking, skydiving, collecting, rock-climbing
Nationality: malaysian, nigerian, french, thai
1. Nationality:thai is between Hobby:collecting and Nationality:nigerian##2
2. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:french is on the right of Nationality:malaysian##1
4. Hobby:hiking is on the left of Nationality:malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | hiking | collecting | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | thai   | malaysian | french       |

