2. Nationality:american is between Nationality:german and Food:cabbage##2
3. Nationality:german is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Food:grapes##1
5. Food:cabbage == Nationality:egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | banana    | nectarine | cabbage   | grapes  |
| Nationality   | german | american   | egyptian | italian |

