2. Pet:guinea-pig is between Sport:skiing and Pet:dog##2
3. Sport:snowboarding is on the far right##1
4. Pet:guinea-pig is on the right of Sport:ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | dog   | guinea-pig    | goldfish       | rabbit   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | badminton | skiing | snowboarding |

